}, {\"sentence\": \"'A lot of girls do not work as hard.\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 809, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 788}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's hard too because of SafeSport.\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SafeSport\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coaches can not get on athletes which in some ways is really good but at the same time, to get to where you need to be in gymnastics you do have to be\\u2026 a little aggressive, a little intense.'\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 1037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Coaches\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"some ways\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 896}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Biles appeared to hit back at Skinner's comments in her celebration post on Instagram after winning her first gold in Paris as she posted a photo of her team with their medals alongside the caption: 'Lack of talent, lazy, Olympic champions.'\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1119, \"end\": 1128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.655174867312723e-25, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999895899236, \"rank\": 1.040996459210671e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"Skinner's comments\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"her celebration post\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"her first gold\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"a photo\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"her team\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1200}, {\"ngram\": \"their medals\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"the caption\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"talent\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Skinner has since issued an for her comment, claiming that she was comparing the current Olympic team to the 2021 Olympic team she competed with that was guided by the controversial coaching regime of gymnastics coach Marta Karolyi.\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1504, \"end\": 1517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rta_K\\u00e1rolyi\", \"score\": 0.9999999382885126, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marta Karolyi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rta_K\\u00e1rolyi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rta_K\\u00e1rolyi\"}, {\"begin\": 1504, \"end\": 1517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rta_K\\u00e1rolyi\", \"score\": 0.9999999382885126, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marta Karolyi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rta_K\\u00e1rolyi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rta_K\\u00e1rolyi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Skinner\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"her comment\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"the current Olympic team\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1387}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2021 Olympic team\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversial coaching regime\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Upon reflection, I was comparing the 'Marta Era' to the current era,' she posted on Instagram.\", \"from\": 